## Full Text Search

No extension needed — built into PostgreSQL.

```sql
-- Add a tsvector column for fast search
ALTER TABLE posts ADD COLUMN fts TSVECTOR
  GENERATED ALWAYS AS (to_tsvector('english', COALESCE(title, '') || ' ' || COALESCE(content, ''))) STORED;

CREATE INDEX posts_fts_idx ON posts USING gin(fts);
```

```typescript
// Search from Next.js
const { data } = await supabase
  .from('posts')
  .select()
  .textSearch('fts', query, { type: 'websearch' })
// 'websearch' supports AND, OR, - operators like real search engines
```

